This program requires pyqt4 (but should also work with pyqt5), mutagen and python-pylast.
Example for apt-get:
sudo apt-get install python-pyqt4 python-mutagen python-pylast

Additionally, for Spotify support, pyspotify is needed.
See their site for further information:
https://pyspotify.mopidy.com/en/latest/installation/

After this, fill out the needed information in the example_config.json and rename it to config.json.